Title: MARS NEEDS MOMS Trailer #1
Comment: This is to all the people who are repeatedly bashing the film just by how "bad" it looks. Yes, it doesn't look as colorful and/or cartoon-y like Toy Story or Tangled, but that, I believe, was to be expected coming from the same studio behind Polar Express and A Christmas Carol. Besides, you can't just judge a movie by its imagery, like how you can't judge a book simply by its cover. One must analyze a motion picture by its own merits; that also holds true to all other movies in existence.
